{"tid":469237,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★裁員一定炒IT ! 銀行高層 :舊一批人不能轉型，留在公司只會成為『冗員』","createTime":"2017-11-15T06:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T11:06:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"cd81780a2a3637b58b91680b4fe1ee77f989a070","tid":469237,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:15:49.000Z","msg":"互聯網世代，加上金融科技﹙FinTech﹚急速冒起，銀行對IT人員理應「求才若渴」，但時不時都聽到，各大銀行乃至金融機構為求「瘦身」，紛紛對IT部門「落刀」。<br />\n<br />\n中信銀行（國際）資訊科技及營運總監梁建文則認為，正正因為現今科技日新月異，銀行使用的技術不斷革新，未能轉型的IT員工更容易被時代淘汰。他直言︰「現在銀行推出新產品都希望在手機上運作，相反不斷關閉銀行分行，即是銀行不再需要編寫出納系統的IT人，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果舊一批人不能轉型，只會留在公司成為『冗員』。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/經濟/132558/裁員一定炒IT先-銀行高層現身說法-人才短缺問題好嚴重\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%2F132558%2F%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%82%92IT%E5%85%88-%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB%E8%AA%AA%E6%B3%95-%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E7%9F%AD%E7%BC%BA%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E5%A5%BD%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D&d=sN1xzYXJtnc%2F%2F0sNkt83G3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=00b7f138\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/經濟/132558/裁員一定炒IT先-銀行高層現身說法-人才短缺問題好嚴重</a>"},{"pid":"0bb74062665c133af9b1f58e14fa606c546a13d6","tid":469237,"uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:16:05.000Z","msg":"HK No IT"},{"pid":"c2de4fc2ec72398a6810c75dcfd91a42c71b936d","tid":469237,"uid":28831,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:16:59.000Z","msg":"班高層先係轉型唔到既冗員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f8c6c21d55c1a9a7cb6a45e821de3eb673dff3","tid":469237,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">銀行不再需要編寫出納系統的IT人</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /