%2Fcontent%2F1660000%2F1661147%2Fit_thumb_20170214_J_1024.jpg&h=b0e2ba47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">this is HK</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhk 係再乘7.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f296f09fa3e641df58188e673757f42ad1751441","tid":469237,"uid":84436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:28:32.000Z","msg":"做個政府文員仲好<br />\n<br />\n畢業時 ACO(政府工既文員-助理文書主任) IT(support,infra,si,coder)<br />\nACO: 起薪近15K <br />\nIT\t:IVE/UGRAD 平均12-17K 左近<br />\n<br />\nACO: 每日一般6點前走人,很少OT,OT好似都可以報,放工唔洗諗公司野<br />\nIT\t:每日一般7-8點左右走人,常常OT,仲要晚上隨時收call support,check email<br />\n<br />\n到40中<br />\nACO :升上CO(pt16-21), CO人工近40K(40K係未計通脹 每年再加幾%),工作如常 幾年換一次位, 好似22日假,強積金供出面好多,又可以申請公屋居屋,不用擔心住屋醫療<br />\nIT人 :通常都係30-4XK左右 ,工作如常 OTOT, IT人多數合約工 好少福利...開始outdated,跟唔上後生, 除時被炒又搵工,租屋比較安全<br />\n<br />\n到50中<br />\nCO好運升上SCO人工50K左右(未計通脹 每年再加幾%),安守本份,不會比人炒,等到65歲退休.福利照舊 不怕經濟起伏<br />\n<br />\nIT人,晉升不明朗,可能經過被炒N次 已轉行,市場上新職位中意請FG, 人工變動好大,可能都係落手落腳前線位 ,少數可能上到管理職位<br />\n<br />\n到65歲<br />\nCO/SCO :光榮退休 服務政府大眾40年,有好既退休保障(每個月供既(25+5)%強積金,退休就一大筆)<br />\nIT :不知道<br />\n<br />\nACO睇落普普通通 但做左20年既人到中年後一般都會有40-50K(計埋通脤),<br />\n20年到就排隊升CO又多萬幾<br />\n<br />\n1.唔會怕中年失業,可以keep住升職and加人工<br />\n2.可以住緊用公務員隊申請既公屋, 唔洗煩住屋問題 <br />\n3.有2X日假,請假又唔難批<br />\n4.每月有2X%強積金幫你供 <br />\n5.朝9晚6少OT,就算要OT都可似claim返 <br />\n6.唔洗擦鞋保住份工,有理既可以話返上司轉頭<br />\n7.放工唔洗keep住進修,怕比後生取代<br />\n8.work life balance,放工就放工去邊玩,照顧屋企人就得唔會比工作搞到冇曬私人時間<br />\n9.幾年換一次位,有好有唔好,但唔洗一世做同一個位同一樣野<br />\n10.唔會好似IT咁 讀書又一班仔,做野又一班仔,女都唔易識 <br />\n<br />\n2A3O officer,AP , EO ,紀律部隊更加比做IT 有前途<br />\npoint 22 以上好似仲可以申請供樓資助,約10年 每月有幾K 至 1X K<br />\n真正做左政府工,就明白有幾好 同穩定 安全 唔會怕 中年失業連住屋都有問題<br />\n<br />\nIT人都50歲左近就可能中年失業,比平價FG取代<br />\ninfra 上曬aws,cloud<br />\nprogramming 就outsource 印度 東南亞<br />\nsecurity 可判比本地vendor<br />\n留番D tech BA,IT sales 就得<br />\n<br />\n有料既IT真係去外國好過,人地會專重你, 香港就 medic,finance,law..為主, IT可以搵vendor, outsource去平既地方"},{"pid":"7b27dd59b67ce33397b1238f0c981465443f7b10","tid":469237,"uid":19062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T12:01:18.000Z","msg":"人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"13f7af41505d659696b3a96971b048108cd89094","tid":469237,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T12:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日劇bloody mondey，主角IT狗，用呢啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imtx.me/media/uploads/2008/12/bloodymonday-04.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimtx.me%2Fmedia%2Fuploads%2F2008%2F12%2Fbloodymonday-04.png&h=e941efd9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n用linux"},{"pid":"6a02dbc116f9eee678a184c85c935e3d7f37330d","tid":469237,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T06:45:23.000Z","msg":"bingo"},{"pid":"530dde52e23a5d70731ecc6f48403e6ef7432e58","tid":469237,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e235f3abeb9f73db80ba34213575465f2a6c385","tid":469237,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T06:51:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7c8b50ff098a6008afb563923872ac1dd9c2147e","tid":469237,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:27:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>push</blockquote><br />\nx2"},{"pid":"2f7ef9bab72fccf95dc7cf69ab1b0d14230d1fde","tid":469237,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>push</blockquote><br />\nx2</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d54fb397302776ffba91d5e4fbdfce832cdfeb4","tid":469237,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:53:37.000Z","msg":"it = condom"},{"pid":"47ca32a10856f05d3d21ea7a06541f740f729d63","tid":469237,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20